name: KTechlab Circuit Design File
summary: Learn about .CIRCUIT files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: KTechlab circuit designs can be simulated in the software. They can also be manipulated using low-level programming languages.

description: XML-formatted circuit design file created by KTechlab, a Linux KDE program used for diagramming microcontrollers and other electronics; stores descriptions of electronic components, connections, and the circuit layout.
